# Flat File Structure

The [[Salesforce.com]] platform enforces a flat file structure when deploying [[Apex]] code.  The Force.com IDE assumes [[BidirectionalDeployment]], which encourages developers to follow this convention.  Thus, hierarchical packages structures are avoided.

